# This is where you build GameHub.
#
# Each module's exercise.md will tell you exactly what to create here.
# By the end of the course, this folder will contain all 5 services.
#
# Expected final structure:
#
# services/
# ├── user-service/          (Module 2)
# ├── game-service/          (Module 2)
# ├── activity-service/      (Module 3)
# ├── notification-service/  (Module 4 — Node.js + SQLite, always local)
# └── logging-service/       (Module 4 — GDPR consent + Kafka consumer)
